title: Grateful Dead Live at The Omni on 1995-03-29
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Row Jimmy, Walkin' Blues, Jack A Roe, Mama Tried*-> Mexicali Blues-> Brown Eyed Women, Cassidy

Set 2

Unbroken Chain, Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower-, Corinna-> Mathilda-> Drums-> Space-> I Need A Miracle-> Standing On the Moon-> Not Fade Away, E: U.S. Blues

* Weir on acoustic
